            Determine world_size from mesh
            Calculate base_size = global_shape[shard_dimension] / world_size
            Calculate remainder = global_shape[shard_dimension] % world_size
            
            local_dim_size = base_size
            If rank < remainder:
                local_dim_size = local_dim_size + 1
                
            Create local_shape as copy of global_shape
            Set local_shape[shard_dimension] to local_dim_size
            Return local_shape
