Get Coordinate
Pseudocode
    Function get_coordinate(rank):
        Input: Flat rank ID (e.g., 5)
        Output: N-D coordinate vector (e.g., [1, 1] for a 4x4 mesh)
        
        Initialize an empty coordinate list
        Temporary_rank = rank
        
        Loop through mesh_shape in reverse order:
            Dimension_size = size of the current dimension
            Component = Temporary_rank % Dimension_size
            Prepend Component to the coordinate list
            Temporary_rank = Temporary_rank / Dimension_size
            
        Return the final coordinate sequence
]

