Pseudocode
    Function initialize_process_groups():
        Determine ndim from mesh_shape
        For each dimension axis (d):
            Calculate stride for this axis
            Group ranks that are adjacent along this specific axis
            Instantiate a ProcessGroupNCCL for each isolated clique
            Store these groups for selective collective operations
