get_rank
Pseudocode
    Function get_rank(coordinate_vector):
        Input: Vector of N-D indices (e.g., [1, 1])
        Output: Flattened rank integer (e.g., 5)
        
        Logic: Convert multi-dimensional indices to a flat index (Row-Major)
        Initialize rank_sum = 0
        Initialize multiplier = 1
        
        Loop through dimensions (i) in reverse order:
            rank_sum = rank_sum + (coordinate_vector[i] * multiplier)
            multiplier = multiplier * mesh_shape[i]
            
        Return rank_sum
]

